code: import axios from'axios';var signup=function signup(username,password){return axios.post('/api/auth/signup',{username:username,password:password}).then(function(response){return response.data;}).catch(function(err){return err.response.data;});};var login=function login(username,password){return axios.post('/api/auth/login',{username:username,password:password}).then(function(response){console.log("services",response.data);return response.data;}).catch(function(err){console.log("service err",err.response.data);return err.response.data;});};var logout=function logout(){return axios.delete('/api/auth/logout').then(function(response){return response.data;}).catch(function(err){return err.response.data;});};export{signup,login,logout};
